snippet.title: Note Ban: Petrol Pump Owners are Unable to Provide Cash Withdrawal Service to People

localized.description:
Demonetisation: Petrol pump owners are unable to provide cash withdrawal service to people. Modi government has decided to use petrol pumps to provide cash upto two thousand rupees with the help of SBI swiping machines.
